HEADWORD: Inflammabillty
<hw>In*flam"ma*bil"l*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>inflammabilite</ets>.]</ety> <def>Susceptibility of taking fire
